    • Method Detail

      • window

        public static GetWindowSupplier window()
        Creates an instance of GetWindowSupplier to get any browser window/tab. When criteria(Criteria) or criteria(String, Predicate) are defined then it returns the first browser window that matches defined criteria. Otherwise it returns most likely the first browser window/tab.
        Returns:
        an instance of GetWindowSupplier

      • window

      • currentWindow

        public static GetWindowSupplier currentWindow()
        Creates an instance of GetWindowSupplier to get current browser window/tab. When criteria(Criteria) or criteria(String, Predicate) or criteriaOr(Criteria[]) or criteriaOnlyOne(Criteria[]) ore criteriaNot(Criteria[])are defined then it returns current browser window/tab after it matches criteria. Otherwise it returns current browser window/tab immediately.
        Returns:
        an instance of GetWindowSupplier
